        },
        "text_ewBnHk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Woman-owned. Lincoln, Nebraska. Quietly brilliant.</strong></p><p>We return the favor.</p><p>Wax | Wane is a woman-owned shop rooted in the belief that the best products don't shout — they deliver. Our collections are chosen with forethought: not only for beauty, but for longevity, function, and understated, underrated excellence.</p><p>Science-backed Korean skincare. Authentic natural crystals. Functional EMF shielding for modern life. Three worlds, one standard: considered, tested, and quietly brilliant.</p><p>Ancestors looked to the gods. Today, we look inward. We believe the right objects — worn, used, or placed with intention — can fine-tune your mental state, reduce stress, and create space in a world that rarely does. When your mood shifts, so does everything around you.</p><p>Using science to refine the magic. Innovation built for longevity. Products that return the favor.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_NeWhjG": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
